## Usage

### Minimal

```terraform
resource "system_user" "johndoe" {
  name = "johndoe"
}
```

### Optional home and shell

```terraform
resource "system_user" "johndoe" {
  name  = "johndoe"
  home  = "/home/johndoe"
  shell = "/usr/bin/zsh"
}
```

### Explicit uid

```terraform
resource "system_user" "johndoe" {
  name = "johndoe"
  uid  = 1001
}
```

### System user

```terraform
resource "system_user" "nginx" {
  name   = "nginx"
  system = true
}
```

### User group with explicit gid

```terraform
resource "system_user" "nginx" {
  name   = "nginx"
  gid    = 201
  system = true
}
```

